    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chiral 是一款科幻心理恐怖/喜剧第一人称益智游戏，您将扮演一个罐子中的无实体大脑，与数字 AI 同伴配对。你们将一起穿越镜子、激光和重力谜题的迷宫，挑战您的空间推理能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/a87f0b33fc6588ee898a8adb4daabbe3.poster.avif?t=1764864574\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/a87f0b33fc6588ee898a8adb4daabbe3.webm?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/a87f0b33fc6588ee898a8adb4daabbe3.mp4?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过“常规”大脑转移程序后，您会发现自己身处罐子中，但别担心——您仍然是公司的宝贵资产！当您穿越诡异而迷人的关卡时，您会遇到令人费解的空间谜题和腐败的机器人经理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/e02dd6178402ecf42a8852eb68400e7c.poster.avif?t=1764864574\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/e02dd6178402ecf42a8852eb68400e7c.webm?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/e02dd6178402ecf42a8852eb68400e7c.mp4?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特点：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空间谜题：用复杂的镜子、激光和重力挑战测试您的智力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑色幽默：享受充满恐怖而喜剧色彩的故事情节。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特机制：利用您的能力穿过镜子、操纵物体、改变重力等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大气世界：沉浸在令人不安的令人愉悦的企业反乌托邦中，以野蛮主义为基础，并加入一些卡通增强现实。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/59a55174118b4971980fe89cbda6f51a.poster.avif?t=1764864574\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/59a55174118b4971980fe89cbda6f51a.webm?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/59a55174118b4971980fe89cbda6f51a.mp4?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入 Chiral 并拥抱疯狂。你的大脑将永远不再一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/3fe40ff634b042389d418e84d6821fc6.poster.avif?t=1764864574\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/3fe40ff634b042389d418e84d6821fc6.webm?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106330/extras/3fe40ff634b042389d418e84d6821fc6.mp4?t=1764864574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
